  "version": "1.0.0",
  "name": "ObservationExtractDemo",
  "title": "Observation Extraction Demo (Vital Signs)",
  "status": "draft",
  "description": "Demonstrates SDC Observation-based extraction (sdc-questionnaire-observationExtract). Completed answers below the flagged group are extracted as Observation resources. Body weight/height/temperature carry questionnaire-unit and extract as Quantity; smoking status extracts as a CodeableConcept. The 'Internal note' item sets the flag to false to suppress extraction even though it carries a code.",
  "item": [
